    <i>Shift + move</i> - sprint

    <i>Esc</i>
    - pause menu / exit book

    <i>Z (hold)</i> - camera zoom

    <i>L. Ctrl (hold,
    while aiming at captioned image)</i> - Hover UI interactive mode'
